00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:48.020
Is an act of futurism.

00:27:48.020 --> 00:27:51.460
You are, it's an
optimistic hopeful act,

00:27:51.460 --> 00:27:54.910
as well as a creative
act as well.

00:27:54.910 --> 00:27:57.480
Nora, in your work,
